=====Usage notes=====
The verb ''lay'' is sometimes used interchangeably with the corresponding intransitive verb {{m|en|lie}} in informal spoken settings. This can lead to nonstandard constructions which are sometimes objected to. This usage is common in speech but rarely found in edited writing or in more formal spoken situations.

